  "texts": [
    "Beyond quantitative improvements, DRaFT-Q exhibits qualitative improvements in reasoning.",
    "Manual inspection of model outputs shows that DRaFT-Q generates reasoning chains with fewer hallucinations and more structured intermediate steps.",
    "For example, on arithmetic multi-step problems, the model explicitly performs intermediate operations before arriving at a final numeric answer, rather than guessing.0 100 200 1 1.5 2 Training Steps Loss (a) DRaFT-Q loss curve on GSM8K.",
