    "- LLaMA-2-7B and 13B Dialogue TasksWe evaluated DRaFT-Q on LLaMA-2-7B using OpenAssistant and OpenHermes datasets and LLaMA-2-13B using UltraChat (HF-H4/ultrachat_200k)."
